---
title: Creamy Zucchini & Pork Sausage Risotto with Sun-Dried Tomato Topping & Parmesan
description: Sure, whipping up risotto requires a little extra attention (and stirring), but the results are beyond worth it. Luckily, our chefs have made nailing it easier—and tastier—than ever. This version is chock full of savory pork sausage, tender zucchini, and of course lots of Parmesan. But what sets this one apart is a finishing touch of dollops of a tangy, umami-packed sun-dried tomato topping that beautifully offsets the richness. We know, we know: We had you at “risotto.”
